reviewText: Awesome collectors item for a huge Rockets Fan

If you haven't ordered this Video
you are missing a treat. The Houston
Rockets road to the NBA Championship
in 1993 is remarkable. Akeem Olajuwon
Kenny the (Jet) Smith, Cedric Maxwell,
make for a magnificent video. Akeem
the Dream is fantastic as well as other
key players. This Champinship run
will keep you on the edge of your seat.
This is Basketball at it's finest.!!!
